a.  This circle's circumference, in terms of [`\pi\text{,}`] is [_]{$eval[0]}{15}.

a.  This circle's circumference, rounded to the hundredth place, is [_]{$eval[1]}{15}.

a.  This circle's area, in terms of [`\pi\text{,}`] is [_]{$eval[2]}{15}.

a.  This circle's area, rounded to the hundredth place, is [_]{$eval[3]}{15}.

